{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":22,"_total":22,"_totalPage":3,"_page":2,"posts":[{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":22},{"name":"JavaScript","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/JavaScript/","url":"/async/tags/JavaScript.json","count":28},{"name":"HTML","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/HTML/","url":"/async/tags/HTML.json","count":17},{"name":"响应式","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%BC%8F/","url":"/async/tags/响应式.json","count":3}],"categories":[{"name":"响应式","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%BC%8F/","url":"/async/categories/响应式.json","count":3}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/02/14/responsive-web-design.json","date":1392307200000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":2,"day":14,"name":"responsive-web-design"},"subtitle":"读《响应式Web设计-HTML5和CSS3实践》有感（响应式网页设计部分）","title":"聊聊响应式网页设计","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/02/14/responsive-web-design/","content":"<p>总是在各个地方看到响应式Web设计。一直对其很感兴趣，也只是零零散散的接触，但并没有系统的去学习响应式。这两天读了Ben Frain著（王永强 译）的《响应式Web设计-HTML5和CSS3实践》，收获颇多，在这里记录一下</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":22}],"categories":[{"name":"性能优化","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96/","url":"/async/categories/性能优化.json","count":5}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/02/24/CSS3-animation-optimization.json","date":1393171200000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":2,"day":24,"name":"CSS3-animation-optimization"},"subtitle":"前端性能优化系列","title":"前端性能优化（CSS动画篇）","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/02/24/CSS3-animation-optimization/","content":"<p>最近拜读了一下<a href=\"http://www.html5rocks.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">html5rocks</a>上几位大神写的一篇关于CSS3动画性能优化的文章，学到了很多，在这里记录一下，其中的知识都是来源于这俩篇文章，我只是截取了其中比较关注的内容出来，原文地址<a href=\"http://www.html5rocks.com/en/tutorials/speed/high-performance-animations\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">High Performance Animations</a>及<a href=\"http://www.html5rocks.com/zh/tutorials/speed/layers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Accelerated Rendering in Chrome</a></p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":22}],"categories":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/CSS/","url":"/async/categories/CSS.json","count":6}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/02/09/box-shadow-pix-image.json","date":1391875200000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":2,"day":9,"name":"box-shadow-pix-image"},"subtitle":"使用CSS3属性box-shadow，绘制超级玛丽","title":"使用box-shadow绘制像素画","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/02/09/box-shadow-pix-image/","content":"<p>曾经在codepen.io上看到很多像素画，都是css3实现的，点进去看才知道是使用box-shadow实现的，但是当时并不了解CSS3的box-shadow属性。如今稍微了解了box-shadow属性，并自己绘制了一个超级玛丽</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":22}],"categories":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/CSS/","url":"/async/categories/CSS.json","count":6}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/03/31/css-layout.json","date":1396195200000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":3,"day":31,"name":"css-layout"},"subtitle":"包含块、浮动、相对定位、绝对定位以及布局属性相关关系","title":"CSS布局相关基础知识","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/03/31/css-layout/","content":""},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":22},{"name":"HTML","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/HTML/","url":"/async/tags/HTML.json","count":17}],"categories":[{"name":"翻译","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91/","url":"/async/categories/翻译.json","count":10}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/05/19/google-responsive-design-fundamentals.json","date":1400428800000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":5,"day":19,"name":"google-responsive-design-fundamentals"},"subtitle":"翻译自谷歌Web开发最佳实践手册","title":"响应式Web设计基础","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/05/19/google-responsive-design-fundamentals/","content":"<p>本文所有内容来自<a href=\"https://developers.google.com/web/fundamentals/documentation/multi-device-layouts/rwd-fundamentals\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Responsive Web Design Fundamentals</a></p>\n<p>手机、大屏手机、平板电脑、桌面电脑、游戏控制台、电视、甚至是可穿戴设备，如此多的设备也形成了多种多样的屏幕尺寸。屏幕的大小总在变，我们需要我们的网页今后能够适应任何屏幕尺寸</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":22},{"name":"HTML","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/HTML/","url":"/async/tags/HTML.json","count":17}],"categories":[{"name":"翻译","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91/","url":"/async/categories/翻译.json","count":10}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/05/04/google-style-guide.json","date":1399132800000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":5,"day":4,"name":"google-style-guide"},"subtitle":"写更简洁、更美观的HTML和CSS","title":"Google的HTML/CSS样式指南","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/05/04/google-style-guide/","content":"<p>之前读过网易的NEC，以及百度的前端编码规范，感觉自己HTML和CSS代码写的很烂，这里又读了一下Google的style guide，发现有很多地方值得学习补充，在这里大致上翻译一下</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":22},{"name":"JavaScript","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/JavaScript/","url":"/async/tags/JavaScript.json","count":28},{"name":"HTML","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/HTML/","url":"/async/tags/HTML.json","count":17},{"name":"思考","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83/","url":"/async/tags/思考.json","count":1}],"categories":[{"name":"思考总结","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/","url":"/async/categories/思考总结.json","count":3}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/09/22/learn-fe.json","date":1411315200000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":9,"day":22,"name":"learn-fe"},"subtitle":"一些总结","title":"学前端的一点总结","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/09/22/learn-fe/","content":"<p>最近<a href=\"https://github.com/qiu-deqing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Qiu</a>开了一个<a href=\"https://github.com/qiu-deqing/FE-learning/blob/master/README.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">FE学习经验介绍</a>，并邀请我去写一点东西。感觉这种方式很有意思，趁着闲下来了，就随便扯了一些，希望能帮到想学前端的同学。我自己只是个前端初学者，希望能有更多的前端爱好者一同学习探讨~~</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":22},{"name":"JavaScript","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/JavaScript/","url":"/async/tags/JavaScript.json","count":28},{"name":"HTML","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/HTML/","url":"/async/tags/HTML.json","count":17}],"categories":[{"name":"性能优化","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96/","url":"/async/categories/性能优化.json","count":5}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/03/25/performance-2.json","date":1395676800000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":3,"day":25,"name":"performance-2"},"subtitle":"前端性能优化系列","title":"前端性能优化（JavaScript篇）","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/03/25/performance-2/","content":"<p>最近准备笔试面试题的时候看到很多关于前端性能优化的问题，所以提前调研做做准备，加上我之前写的两篇博客，组成一个新系列</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":22},{"name":"JavaScript","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/JavaScript/","url":"/async/tags/JavaScript.json","count":28},{"name":"HTML","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/HTML/","url":"/async/tags/HTML.json","count":17}],"categories":[{"name":"性能优化","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96/","url":"/async/categories/性能优化.json","count":5}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/03/28/performance-3.json","date":1395936000000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":3,"day":28,"name":"performance-3"},"subtitle":"前端性能优化系列","title":"前端性能优化（JavaScript补充篇）","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/03/28/performance-3/","content":"<p>最近准备笔试面试题的时候看到很多关于前端性能优化的问题，所以提前调研做做准备，加上我之前写的两篇博客，组成一个新系列</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":22},{"name":"JavaScript","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/JavaScript/","url":"/async/tags/JavaScript.json"